ActEconomic Action Plan 2014 Act, No. 1
Combating Counterfeit Products Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day after the Day on which this Order is made as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the two Acts Come into Force
PrecisOrder (1) Fixing the day after the day on which this Order is made as the day on which section 358.1 of the ECONOMIC ACTION PLAN 2014 ACT, NO. 1 chapter 20 of the Statutes of Canada, 2014, COMES INTO FORCE; and (2) Fixing the day after the day on which this Order is made as the day on which sections 27 and 28 of the COMBATING COUNTERFEIT PRODUCTS ACT, chapter 32 of the Statutes of Canada, 2014, COME INTO FORCE.
